9d387afb-a4f0-4e50-b0f8-387c6fb4b59a.77d0fede-6ab4-4b26-a68d-c8e35ad550d7.description=
Adds a flow variable into the local context (available to itself and child flows only)

Input Parameters\:
keyName - the name of the flow variable to use
myValue - the value to assign the flow variable

Responses\:
success - assigned the flow variable

Scriptlet Example\:
[$scriptletContext putGlobal\: $keyName, $myValue];
9d387afb-a4f0-4e50-b0f8-387c6fb4b59a.description=
Add a Server Component to Server Group and Provision a clone server in vCenter.


Inputs\:
 artifactId - Component Id of the Application Tier Component
 userIdentifier - OO Application UUID
 serviceInstanceId - Service Instance of the Blue Print for the given Subscription
 addServers - Number of Server Components to add.

Responses\:
 success - if the command completes execution and its exit code is 0
 failure - otherwise

Result\:
 serverId 		- Server Component Id that was added into CSA
 severGrpId 		- Server Group Component Id where server as added.
